OL,3,C'I thought that was it': Cyclist says
OL,4,Cshe almost died after pothole crash
OL,6,FA woman from Newbury says she almost
OL,7,Fdied after crashing into a pothole
OL,8,Fwhilst riding her bike on a country
OL,9,Froad.
OL,11,FBeckie Hamilton, an experienced
OL,12,Fcyclist, didn't see the pothole whilst
OL,13,Fcycling near Welford in the Berkshire
OL,14,Fcountryside.
OL,16,FShe was thrown from her bike and into
OL,17,Fthe path of an oncoming truck, who had
OL,18,Fto swerve to avoid her.
OL,20,FShe said: "It was a dark evening, got
OL,21,Fgood lights and everything.
