OL,3,C'I thought that was it': Cyclist says
OL,4,Cshe almost died after pothole crash
OL,6,F"And completely out of the blue
OL,7,F'bang', hit the pothole behind me and
OL,8,Fall I remember is I was sliding on my
OL,9,Fhelmet towards an oncoming vehicle.
OL,11,F"I thought that was it, I thought this
OL,12,Fis my time. Couldn't see anyway out of
OL,13,Fit, that's the only thing that went
OL,14,Fthrough my mind."
OL,16,FThe driver got out of his vehicle to
OL,17,Fcheck she was ok.
