OL,3,C'I thought that was it': Cyclist says
OL,4,Cshe almost died after pothole crash
OL,6,FWhilst at the hospital, they found she
OL,7,Fhad injured her ribs, fractured
OL,8,Ffingers and hurt her elbows and
OL,9,Fshoulders.
OL,11,FShe is now urging others to wear a
OL,12,Fhelmet as she believes it saved her
OL,13,Flife.
OL,15,F"Looking back there's nothing I could
OL,16,Fhave done," she said.
OL,18,F"To think you're here and then a few
OL,19,Fdays later, you're just out in the
OL,20,Fsunshine and I thought to myself I
OL,21,Fnearly didn't see this day.
