OL,3,C'I thought that was it': Cyclist says
OL,4,Cshe almost died after pothole crash
OL,6,F"My helmet and the driver without a
OL,7,Fdoubt saved my life.
OL,9,F"I wouldn't be here if it wasn't for
OL,10,Fboth of those things."
OL,12,FA spokesperson for West Berkshire
OL,13,FCouncil said: "We were made aware of
OL,14,Fthis pothole along Welford Road which
OL,15,Fwas assessed and has now been repaired
OL,16,Fwithin the required timeframe in line
OL,17,Fwith our Highway Asset Management
OL,18,Fpolicy."
